            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following edition is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="BDLaethe31"/>.</note>
                <ab xml:lang="gez">
                    በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ አአምን፡
                    በስመ፡ ወልድ፡ አአምን፡ በስመ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                    አአምን፡ በ፫ አካላት፡
                    ወበአ፩ መለኮት፡ ከመ፡
                    ኢትቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሳ፡ ወሥጋሀ፡ ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"></gap>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <ab xml:lang="en">
                    In the name of the Father and the Son.
                    In the name of the Father, I believe.
                    In the name of the Son, I believe.
                    In the name of the Holy Spirit, I believe in three Persons and one Nature.
                    So that you do not approach the soul and body of your maidservant…
                </ab>
            </div>
